{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778467763194,"sessionID":"ses_1eb15cb77ffeCWdAGJ8yaA0emo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"functions.bash:35","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git commit -m \"Obsolete GO:1905353 and GO:0097711, replace by GO:1905349\n\nObsoletion of two redundant ciliary terms with direct replacement:\n- GO:1905353 ciliary transition fiber assembly → GO:1905349 ciliary transition zone assembly\n- GO:0097711 ciliary basal body-plasma membrane docking → GO:1905349 ciliary transition zone assembly\n\nAlso removed starts_with GO:0097711 from GO:0060271 cilium assembly,\nas the replacement term is already part_of cilium assembly.\n\nCloses geneontology/go-ontology#31882\"","description":"Commit obsoletion changes"},"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-go-ontology-agent-config-v9-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-31882 237a9ee] Obsolete GO:1905353 and GO:0097711, replace by GO:1905349\n 1 file changed, 13 insertions(+), 32 deletions(-)\n","metadata":{"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-go-ontology-agent-config-v9-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-31882 237a9ee] Obsolete GO:1905353 and GO:0097711, replace by GO:1905349\n 1 file changed, 13 insertions(+), 32 deletions(-)\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit obsoletion changes","truncated":false},"title":"Commit obsoletion changes","time":{"start":1778467763190,"end":1778467763193}},"id":"prt_e14f0557b001eE8ZHBfw5AY5ji","sessionID":"ses_1eb15cb77ffeCWdAGJ8yaA0emo","messageID":"msg_e14f02323001qUHW4UopalZx5E"}}
