{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778467809121,"sessionID":"ses_1eb15cb77ffeCWdAGJ8yaA0emo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:37","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nFollowing the final decision in #31882, both terms have been obsoleted and replaced by `GO:1905349 ciliary transition zone assembly`:\n- `GO:1905353` ciliary transition fiber assembly\n- `GO:0097711` ciliary basal body-plasma membrane docking\n\nAdditionally, the `starts_with GO:0097711` relationship was removed from `GO:0060271` cilium assembly, as the replacement term is already `part_of` cilium assembly.\n\nAll ontology validation checks (ELK reasoning + full SPARQL QC suite) passed with 0 violations.\n","filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778467809117,"end":1778467809120}},"id":"prt_e14f12731001CwF8wzEwdQelNC","sessionID":"ses_1eb15cb77ffeCWdAGJ8yaA0emo","messageID":"msg_e14f0747b001a7rBApXEcxt1KA"}}
